  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators intend to study the impact of two different preparation regimens for
      colonoscopy (PEG vs sodium picosulphate) on the quality of the endoscopy as well as patient
      tolerability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
